OL,3,CMan jailed for sending threatening
OL,4,Cmessages to deputy first minister
OL,6,FAn east Belfast man who sent
OL,7,Fthreatening online messages to
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland's deputy First
OL,9,FMinister Emma Little-Pengelly and
OL,10,Fsmashed the windows of a party
OL,11,Fcolleague's office has been jailed.
OL,13,FBelfast Crown Court heard how the
OL,14,Fposts on Twitter left Emma Little-
OL,15,FPengelly so scared she considered
OL,16,Fmoving from her home.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/13
