OL,4,Cmessages to deputy first minister
OL,6,FCurragh posted a series of messages on
OL,7,Fhis Twitter feed indicating he was
OL,8,Fresponsible.
OL,10,FIn one, Curragh Tweeted a narrated
OL,11,Fvideo depicting a window breaking with
OL,12,Fthe comment 'Hi DUP remember me' and
OL,13,Falso used an explosion emoji.
OL,15,FIn July the next year, windows were
OL,16,Fagain smashed as well as those from of
OL,17,Fthe next door solicitors' office.
OL,19,FThe court also heard that Curragh
OL,20,Fposted a series of Tweets about Emma
OL,21,FLittle-Pengelly in July 2024.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/13
