OL,3,CMan jailed for sending threatening
OL,4,Cmessages to deputy first minister
OL,6,FOne Tweet said: "Oh by the way Emma
OL,7,Fwhatever your f*****g name is from the
OL,8,FDUP there's a death threat on your
OL,9,Fhead because everyone keeps telling us
OL,10,Fwhere you live.''
OL,12,FHe also posted a video which appeared
OL,13,Fto be pointing in the direction of Ms
OL,14,FLittle-Pengelly's house.
OL,16,FIn this video Curragh can be heard
OL,17,Fsaying "there's Emma from the DUP with
OL,18,Fa death threat on her head from
OL,19,Fmembers of her own party and the
OL,20,Fpeople who she goes shopping to are
OL,21,Ftelling me where she lives'.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/13
