OL,6,FIn another video on the same date,
OL,7,FCurragh said "It's a real shame I
OL,8,Fcan't upload where I am....but I hope
OL,9,Fyou're alive by the time I get
OL,10,Fuploading, Emma.''
OL,12,FOn being made aware of the posts, Mrs
OL,13,FLittle-Pengelly recognised the
OL,14,Fdefendant from his profile photograph
OL,15,Fand recalled meeting him in a local
OL,16,Fshop when he repeated over and over
OL,17,Fagain: "Oh my f*****g God it's Emma
OL,18,FLittle-Pengelly".
