OL,6,FThe court heard on being interviewed
OL,7,FCurragh admitted damaging the office
OL,8,Fin July 2024 and posting online the
OL,9,Fdeputy first minister about Ms Little-
OL,10,FPengelly but denied the criminal
OL,11,Fdamage in December 2023, claiming he
OL,12,Fwould have been in bed at 2am.
OL,14,FBoth Ms Bunting and Mrs Little-
OL,15,FPengelly provided written victim
OL,16,Fimpact statements for the sentencing
OL,17,Fhearing.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/13
