OL,6,FIn her statement, Ms Bunting described
OL,7,Fthe "upset, hurt and fear'' she had
OL,8,Ffelt following the attacks on her
OL,9,FKnock Road constituency office.
OL,11,FShe said her staff mainly used the
OL,12,Fpremises and they "had to change the
OL,13,Fway they worked, the atmosphere at
OL,14,Fwork and the accessibility to the
OL,15,Fpublic'' which all affected her role
OL,16,Fas an MLA.
OL,18,FMs Bunting said that as a result of
OL,19,Fthe attacks her staff "remained in
OL,20,Ffear of violence''.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/13
