OL,6,F"This is a young man who during the
OL,7,Fcourse of a number of interviews
OL,8,Fgiving explanations for the behaviour
OL,9,Fdisplayed entirely irrational thinking.
OL,11,F"He must be personally deterred from
OL,12,Fengaging again in any behaviour of
OL,13,Fthis type.''
OL,15,FJudge Kerr also imposed a seven-year
OL,16,Frestraining order on Curragh and
OL,17,Fwarned him not to have contact
OL,18,Fdirectly or indirectly with his
OL,19,Fvictims.
